\v 14 M…Ď Yinni Gusun…Ē u k…õŐÉsi k…õŐÉsi b…Ďr…Ďru sure Isirelib…Ď s…Ē…Ē. M…Ď t…Ēmbu n…Ēr…Ēbun sub…Ď w…Ďt…Ď k…Ď w…Ēkuru (70.000) b…Ď gu.
\v 15 Yinni Gusun…Ē u win g…Ēr…Ďdo g…Ēr…Ď Yerus…Ďl…õmu…Ē u ye kpeer…Ďsi…Ď. S…Ďn…Ďm m…õ g…Ēr…Ďdo wi, u ye kpeer…Ďsi…Ďm…Ē, Yinni Gusun…Ē u m…õ…õr…Ď, m…Ď u g…ĒŐÉru g…Ēsi…Ď k…ĒŐÉs…Ď yen di. M…Ď u win g…Ēr…Ďdo wi u wuu ge kpeer…Ďsi…Ďm…Ē mi, s…ĒŐÉ…Ēw…Ď u n…õ…õ, n den tur…Ď m…õ, …Ď wun…õn n…Ēmu wun…Ē.
\p N deem…Ď g…Ēr…Ďdo wi, u w…ĎŐÉ…Ďw…Ď ∆Ü…Ēn…Ďni, Yebusin doo soo yer…Ē.
